snippet.textDisplay:
I also tried to order it today and even though their Terms and Conditions state that they accept card payments the only options you get for payment are Bank transfer and by Crypto currency which is sketchy af. When I emailed them and asked why they say you can use a card but you clearly can't they didn't really answer but only said that I could also use Western Union if I wanted to but they recommend bank transfer :D

So yeah, no way to recall your money if they decide to not send you a device. I imagine Arun only got it because they figured out who he is. So as nice as "A Galaxy fold for 400 USD" sounds, it appears to have all the signs of a scam.
